{"tid":1263792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【參與民陣7.1反修例遊行︰北區免費旅遊巴去程服務】","createTime":"2019-06-28T11:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T12:00:20.000Z","uid":267654,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ef821e8d1aeafd4dc68277405e0085cdb905dc3a","tid":1263792,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"【參與民陣7.1反修例遊行︰免費旅遊巴去程服務】(我們需要車長義工，請pm!)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2J6L3ZC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2J6L3ZC&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=0eeaacba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2J6L3ZC</a><br />\n<br />\n無飯盒、無500蚊一日津貼、不用做會員，只想方便各位北區人參加遊行，聽聽北區人聲音！<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年7月1日<br />\n<br />\n下午一時正<br />\n上車地點：A) 上水大會堂、B) 粉嶺華明邨、C) 聯和墟<br />\n<br />\n下午二時三十分 <br />\n參加反修例遊行︰維園&gt;政府總部<br />\n<br />\n報名方法︰<br />\n1）<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2J9cWA9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2J9cWA9&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=ffaa3a49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2J9cWA9</a> 填寫資料<br />\n2）請按上車地點聯絡報名：<br />\n      張小姐（大會堂）55257705 <br />\n      黎小姐（華明邨）65469077<br />\n      陳傳道（聯和墟）60770032  <br />\n查詢：65469077 黎小姐 或 55257705 張小姐<br />\n<br />\n*成功報名者將會收到我們的wts app或來電確認，凡未收到的則視為未能功登記<br />\n由於報名者眾，而安排要細緻，加上全為義工運作，請報名者必必必必必必必須有耐性等候，以免增加義工壓力(義工也要吃飯陪家人)。<br />\n我們最遲於6月30深夜或凌晨回覆。如你真的太擔心因我們太遲回而安排不及，可考慮自行安排交通前往。感謝！<br />\n<br />\n主辦： 北區小節 、 好鄰舍北區教會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/Gb9iZU2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FGb9iZU2&h=9ea519f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d4eb47ae5141774bb432c1fb6732565f0552179","tid":1263792,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:18:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736bbc765bd195b63be2124bec77945c111b85ed","tid":1263792,"uid":259397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:23:39.000Z","msg":"北區小哲係好野黎！👍🏻"},{"pid":"94299a5f28170a342513f921d4ce5be3d50c5d69","tid":1263792,"uid":48379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:28:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfc15a51de34f190884bd7a1605eba617a2b1f85","tid":1263792,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"北區動源呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4645d613c4dd6d0447ad11bf72c9a0ec958141","tid":1263792,"uid":9950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"唔知會唔會好似69 果日唔同地方都有免費車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d560181502d8bfefe8f971c30d3fdf9c90908b1d","tid":1263792,"uid":229289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133831e7c081acd444a2184dcf34699d8dada0b2","tid":1263792,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03785d7e3adeb59862223291401c306e749041ce","tid":1263792,"uid":56366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:42:20.000Z","msg":"多謝你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n北區人一齊企出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相比起市區嘅朋友我哋條路仲更加漫長"},{"pid":"e7d95a34a06e092596ef322cf343b9d98b191b44","tid":1263792,"uid":224106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}